<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-30 03:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6009 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r s BC-BBO-GONZALEZ-COLUMN-T     08-30 0764
