</P>
<P>
   Filming there was set to wrap up by this weekend, but Sims said
she can't tell how the scenes will fit into the movie's plot.
``It's a deep, dark secret here,'' she said.
</P>
<P>
   Ten other movies have filmed scenes on the grounds or in the
