   Phil Brown, ``Catskill Culture: A Mountain Rat's Memories of the
Great Jewish Resort Area'' (Temple University Press, 1998)
</P>
<P>
   Tania Grossinger, ``Growing Up at Grossinger's'' (D. McKay Co.,
1975)
</P>
